This program provides an easy-to-use system for managing a small book inventory. It offers basic functionalities like adding, searching, editing, and buying books. 
It is a simple example of object-oriented programming (OOP) concepts in C++ and could be further enhanced with more features like file handling, input validation, and more sophisticated error handling.

